title: Tamil Nadu politics: PM Narendra Modi to meet Tamil Nadu CM E Palaniswami shortly
text:
Tamil Nadu politics: PM Narendra Modi to meet Tamil Nadu CM E Palaniswami shortly Tamil Nadu politics: PM Narendra Modi to meet Tamil Nadu CM E Palaniswami shortly Prime Minister Narendra Modi will meet Tamil Nadu Chief Minister E Palaniswami shortly on the birth anniversary of former Tamil Nadu CM Jayalalithaa. Further details awaited. By: FE Online | New Delhi | Published: February 24, 2017 8:35 PM Prime Minister Narendra Modi. Source: Reuters 
Prime Minister Narendra Modi will meet Tamil Nadu Chief Minister E Palaniswami shortly on the birth anniversary of former Tamil Nadu CM Jayalalithaa. 
Further details awaited.
